entry.title: Morex Lyon French Wired Ribbon (Silky Satin/Gold Tones) - 3/8" ; 27 Yards
entry.summary:
Vendor: Morex
Type: Ribbon
Price: 12.21

Our lyon french wired silky satin ribbon with gold tones comes in 97 beautiful colors. Available in 3/8" width on 27 yard spools and 5/8", 1", 1-1/2" & 2-3/8" on 27 and 100 yard spools. This ribbon is perfect for any floral application as well as invitations, gift wrap, gift baskets and various other craft designs.
(Product Characteristic: Solid Color Ribbon) / (Fabric Content: 100% Acetate Yarn)
